<body>
  <header>
    <h1>PonyBreeds API </h1>
  </header>

  <main>
    <div>
      <nav >
        <ul class="menu">
          <h1><%= link_to 'API docs', rswag_ui_path %></h1>
          <h1><a target="_blank" href="https://github.com/napster235/pony_breed_api">GitHub</a></h1>
        </ul>
      </nav>
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Overview</h2>
        <p>
          The PonyBreed API provides an interface for the PonyBreeds ruby gem. At the moment, the API is hosted on Render using a free tier, so the first request might be a bit slow.
          In order to access the API you don't need a key, and it free to use. You can use this API to learn new things, practice or build a small project.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</body>
